      "reading_order": 8,
      "text": "Once of the most common causes\nof discrimination in India is\nthe caste system . Untouchability\nis one of the cruelest expressions\nof such discrimination . The Dalits\nwere denied equal opportunities\nin education, employment and\nhealthcare for long. But the efforts\nof Dr BR Ambedkar encouraged\nmany others to speak up in\nfavour of removing the practices\nof untouchability in India. Finally\nArticle 17 of the constitution of\nIndia made the practice of\nuntouchability an offence\npunishable by law."
    },
